'''Dream flower potion''' was a strong medicine found on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]]. It was a powerful sedative that could put even the largest organisms into a deep sleep. [[Gonster]] of the [[Twin Hills]] was known to possess a batch of this potion, kept alongside its other ingredients. The [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] and [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]] obtained a vial of Dream flower potion for use on the [[Raich]] during his [[Raich crisis|temporary return]]. Unfortunately for the two Ewoks, Wicket inadvertently alerted the Raich to his presence while trying to place the potion in his water bowl, and the potion was lost in the process.

